<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{بِسْمِ اللهِ الرَّحْمَنِ الرَّحِيمِ}</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">الْفَصْلُ الثَّانِي مِنْ كِتَابِ العِبَادَات:</span> <span class="c3">{الصَّلَاة}</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">ويشتمل على أَرْبَعَةٍ وعِشرينَ بَابًا وهي:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>مَشْرُوعِيَّة اَلصَّلَاة ... حُكْم اَلصَّلَاة<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>حُكْم تَارِك اَلصَّلَاة ... شُرُوط وُجُوب اَلصَّلَاة<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>شُرُوط صِحَّة اَلصَّلَاة ... أَرْكَان وَفَرَائِض اَلصَّلَاة<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَاجِبَات اَلصَّلَاة ... سُنَن اَلصَّلَاة<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>مُبَاحَات اَلصَّلَاة ... مَكْرُوهَات اَلصَّلَاة<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>مُبْطِلَات اَلصَّلَاة ... أنواع الصلاة<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>الشَّك فِي الصَّلَاة ... أَحْكَام الْبِنَاء عَلَى الصَّلَاة<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>مَا تُخَالِف بِهِ اَلْمَرْأَة اَلرَّجُل فِي اَلصَّلَاة ... آدَاب وَأَحْكَام الْمَسَاجِد<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>صَلَاةُ اَلْجَمَاعَة ... صَلَاة اَلْمَرِيض<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>صَلَاةُ الْمُسَافِر ... صَلَاة اَلْخَوْف<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>الْقُنُوتُ فِي اَلصَّلَاة ... سُجُود اَلسَّهْو<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>سُجُود اَلتِّلَاوَة ... سُجُود الشُّكْر<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>